F^{q}\left(x,\eta,\Delta_{\perp}^{2}\right)=\int\dif^{2}\boldsymbol{k_{\perp}}\mathcal{F}^{q}\left(x,\boldsymbol{k_{\perp}};\eta,\boldsymbol{\Delta_{\perp}}\right)\label{eq:2.82}
