\begin_layout Subsection
夸克算符
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对一个四分量的费米场算符
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

，使用投影算符得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi=\psi_{+}+\psi_{-},\quad\psi_{\pm}\equiv\Pi^{\pm}\psi,\quad\Pi_{\pm}\equiv\frac{1}{2}\gamma^{\mp}\gamma^{\pm}.
\]

\end_inset

分解得到的两个分量
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{\pm}$
\end_inset

的光锥自旋为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Sigma^{-+}\psi_{\pm}=\pm\frac{1}{2}\psi_{\pm}
\]

\end_inset

这里
\begin_inset Formula $\Sigma^{\mu\nu}\equiv\frac{1}{4}\left[\gamma^{\mu},\gamma^{\nu}\right]$
\end_inset

是自旋张量。由于费米子场的量纲为
\begin_inset Formula $d=3/2$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{+}$
\end_inset

的自旋为
\begin_inset Formula $1/2$
\end_inset

，所以扭度为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{-}$
\end_inset

的自旋为
\begin_inset Formula $-1/2$
\end_inset

，所以扭度为
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

。因此，只有
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{+}$
\end_inset

会进入最低扭度的非定域算符。从四分量到 Weyl 旋量，“good”部分产生两个独立的场
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi_{+\uparrow}=\frac{1}{2}\left(1+\gamma^{5}\right)\psi_{+},\quad\psi_{+\downarrow}=\frac{1}{2}\left(1-\gamma^{5}\right)\psi_{+},
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{+\uparrow}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{+\downarrow}$
\end_inset

只有一个分量不为零，描述一个拥有确定螺旋度的状态。螺旋度算符习惯上定义为（Appendix A.2）
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
h\equiv\frac{1}{2}\bar{e}_{\perp}^{i}e_{\perp}^{j}\Sigma^{ij}=i\Sigma^{12},\quad e_{\perp}^{i}=\left(\bar{e}_{\perp}^{i}\right)^{*}=\left(1,i\right),
\]

\end_inset

螺旋度的本征值为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
h\psi_{+\uparrow}=\frac{1}{2}\psi_{+\uparrow},\quad h\psi_{+\downarrow}=-\frac{1}{2}\psi_{+\downarrow},
\]

\end_inset

在weyl 表象下
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi_{+\uparrow}=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\lambda_{\uparrow}\\
0
\end{array}\right),\quad\psi_{+\downarrow}=\left(\begin{array}{c}
0\\
\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

其中Weyl 旋量
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lambda_{\uparrow}\sim\left(\begin{array}{c}
1\\
0
\end{array}\right),\quad\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}\sim\left(\begin{array}{c}
0\\
1
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

分别是洛伦兹群的
\begin_inset Formula $\left(0,\frac{1}{2}\right)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\frac{1}{2},0\right)$
\end_inset

表示。使用它们可以构造所有双粒子领头阶扭度算符，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\frac{1}{2},0\right)\otimes\left(\frac{1}{2},0\right)=\left(0,0\right)\oplus\left(1,0\right),\quad\left(\frac{1}{2},0\right)\otimes\left(0,\frac{1}{2}\right)=\left(\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2}\right).
\]

\end_inset

可以构造四个不同的组合，把它们写回到四维形式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lambda_{\uparrow}^{*}\lambda_{\uparrow}\pm\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}^{*}\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\bar{\psi}\left\{ \begin{array}{c}
\gamma^{+}\\
\gamma^{+}\gamma^{5}
\end{array}\right\} \psi,\quad\lambda_{\uparrow}^{*}\chi_{\downarrow}\pm\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}^{*}\lambda_{\uparrow}=\frac{i}{\sqrt{2}}\bar{\psi}\left\{ \begin{array}{c}
i\sigma^{+2}\\
\sigma^{+1}
\end{array}\right\} \psi,
\]

\end_inset

后两个算符
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{\uparrow}^{*}\chi_{\downarrow}\pm\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}^{*}\lambda_{\uparrow}$
\end_inset

仅仅是一个二维矢量的两个分量。注意到
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

并不是独立的，
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}\sigma^{\mu\nu}=\frac{i}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

不作为一个可能的狄拉克结构。所以领头阶扭度的bilocal 夸克算符为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \mathcal{O}^{qq}\left(z_{1}^{-},z_{2}^{-}\right)=\bar{\psi}\left(z_{1}^{-}\right)\left[z_{1}^{-},z_{2}^{-}\right]\gamma^{+}\psi\left(z_{2}^{-}\right)\\
 & \tilde{\mathcal{O}}^{qq}\left(z_{1}^{-},z_{2}^{-}\right)=\bar{\psi}\left(z_{1}^{-}\right)\left[z_{1}^{-},z_{2}^{-}\right]\gamma^{+}\gamma^{5}\psi\left(z_{2}^{-}\right)\\
 & \mathcal{T}_{\mu}^{qq}\left(z_{1}^{-},z_{2}^{-}\right)=\bar{\psi}\left(z_{1}^{-}\right)\left[z_{1}^{-},z_{2}^{-}\right]\sigma_{\phantom{+}\mu}^{+\perp}\psi\left(z_{2}^{-}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

这里添加了规范链接，以使得算符是明显规范不变的，即使不再光锥规范
\begin_inset Formula $A^{+}=0$
\end_inset

中。如在介绍中讨论的，物理观测量中的路径排序的指数来自于末态（DIS）和初态（DY）相互作用。
\end_layout

