 矩阵，Dirac双旋量可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{\lambda}(p)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{E_{p}+m}w_{\lambda}\\
\sqrt{E_{p}-m}\left(\vec{n}\cdot\vec{\sigma}\right)w_{\lambda}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

它定义了一个粒子，能量是
\begin_inset Formula $E_{p}$
\end_inset

，动量为
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}$
\end_inset

,沿着单位矢量
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{n}\equiv\vec{p}/\sqrt{\vec{p}^{2}}$
\end_inset

的方向运动。Weyl 旋量
\begin_inset Formula $w_{\lambda}$
\end_inset

是螺旋度算符的本征函数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
回忆起 Pauli-Lubanski 矢量为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W^{\mu}=\frac{1}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}P_{\nu}M_{\rho\sigma}
\]

\end_inset

在粒子静止系中的螺旋度算符为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
h=-\frac{i}{m}W^{3}=i\Sigma^{12}=\frac{1}{2}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\sigma^{3} & 0\\
0 & \sigma^{3}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

其中使用了关系
\begin_inset Formula $\Sigma^{\mu\nu}=\frac{1}{4}\left[\gamma^{\mu},\gamma^{\nu}\right]$
\end_inset

来写出自旋矩阵的表示。由于在粒子静止系中，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{\lambda}(0)=\sqrt{2m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
w_{\lambda}\\
0
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

螺旋度的本征方程
\begin_inset Formula $hu_{\lambda}(0)=\lambda u_{\lambda}(0)$
\end_inset

的解为（本征值为
\begin_inset Formula $+\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $-\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

）：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
w_{\uparrow}(0)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
1\\
0
\end{array}\right),\quad w_{\downarrow}(0)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
0\\
1
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

如果选择一个不同的方向定义极化状态，本征方程为
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}\left(\vec{n}\cdot\vec{\sigma}\right)w^{\lambda}=\lambda w^{\lambda}$
\end_inset

。解变成:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
w_{\uparrow} & =\left(\begin{array}{c}
\cos\frac{\theta}{2}\\
\sin\frac{\theta}{2}e^{i\phi}
\end{array}\right)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\lvert\vec{p}\rvert\left(\lvert\vec{p}\rvert+p^{3}\right)}}\left(\begin{array}{c}
\lvert\vec{p}\rvert+p^{3}\\
p_{\perp}
\end{array}\right)\\
w_{\downarrow} & =\left(\begin{array}{c}
-\sin\frac{\theta}{2}e^{-i\phi}\\
\cos\frac{\theta}{2}
\end{array}\right)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\lvert\vec{p}\rvert\left(\lvert\vec{p}\rvert+p^{3}\right)}}\left(\begin{array}{c}
-\bar{p}_{\perp}\\
\lvert\vec{p}\rvert+p^{3}
\end{array}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

这些 Weyl 旋量被归一化为
\begin_inset Formula $w_{\lambda^{\prime}}^{\ast}w_{\lambda}=\delta_{\lambda^{\prime}\lambda}$
\end_inset

。这里的
\begin_inset Formula $(\theta,\phi)$
\end_inset

是polar and azimuthal angels ，指定矢量
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{n}$
\end_inset

的方向。在方程中，还使用了 holomorphic (全纯)和 anti-holomorphic 动量，用垂直于
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

轴的分量定义。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{\perp}\equiv p^{x}+ip^{y},\quad\bar{p}_{\perp}\equiv p^{x}-ip^{y}
\]

\end_inset

总的 Dirac bispinor 被归一化为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{u}_{\lambda}(p)u_{\lambda^{\prime}}(p)=2m\delta_{\lambda\lambda^{\prime}}
\]

\end_inset

